OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777849379
OL,3,CTwo people dead after 'suspicious'
OL,4,Cexplosion in house
OL,6,FTwo people have died following an
OL,7,Fexplosion at a residential address in
OL,8,FBristol, police have said.
OL,10,FThe cause is being treated as
OL,11,Fsuspicious and a major incident has
OL,12,Fbeen declared, Avon and Somerset
OL,13,FPolice said in a statement.
OL,15,FThe explosion was reported on
OL,16,FSterncourt Road, in the Frenchay area
OL,17,Fof Bristol, at about 6.30am on Sunday.
OL,19,FIt is not being treated as a suspected
OL,20,Fterrorist incident, police said.
