OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Given the recent change to the UK
OL,12,Fthreat level, we would like to
OL,13,Freassure the public from the outset we
OL,14,Fare not treating this as a suspected
OL,15,Fterrorist incident," the force said.
OL,17,FThe two people who died are both
OL,18,Fadults and their families have been
OL,19,Fupdated, the police said.
