OL,3,CTwo people dead after 'suspicious'
OL,4,Cexplosion in house
OL,6,FOfficers are not looking for anyone
OL,7,Felse in connection with the explosion
OL,8,Fand a cordon remains in place at the
OL,9,Fscene.
OL,11,FResidents living within an area
OL,12,Fcordoned off by police are being
OL,13,Fevacuated to a temporary rest centre.
